      "text": "{user}さん、そんなに慌ててどうしたんですか",
      "startTime": 2.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 7.13333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "さくら！　事故に遭ったって本当なのか！\n無事なのか！？",
      "startTime": 9.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 9.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "きゃあああっ！",
      "startTime": 11.166666666666666,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_slap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 200.00000000000108,
          "startTime": 11.366666666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 13.833333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "ビンタしちゃってすみません……\nもの凄い形相で迫ってきたので、つい……",
      "startTime": 18.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いてて……いや、こっちこそ驚かせてすまない\nそれで体は大丈夫なのか？",
      "startTime": 29,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 32.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと転んでかすり傷を作っただけです",
      "startTime": 32.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "考え事をしながら歩いていたら\n赤信号に気付かずに横断歩道に出てしまって……",
      "startTime": 38.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 43.43333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "それで車にはねられそうになって転んじゃったんです",
      "startTime": 43.43333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 48.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "一歩間違えれば大怪我じゃないか！\n何をしてるんだ、さくら！",
      "startTime": 50.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 52.93333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　あ、あの、{user}さん？",
      "startTime": 52.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、いや……大声を出して悪かった\nでも頼むから事故にだけは気をつけてくれ",
      "startTime": 63.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 67.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "はい……分かりました……",
      "startTime": 67.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 71.36666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、大丈夫ですか？\n顔色が真っ青です",
      "startTime": 75.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、すまない……\nちょっとあの時のことを思い出してしまってな",
      "startTime": 80.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 84.23333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "あの時のことって、もしかして\n麻奈さんが事故に遭った日のことですか？",
      "startTime": 88.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 91.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "もしよかったら\nその時のことを聞かせてもらえませんか？",
      "startTime": 93.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、ちゃんと話したことはなかったな\n麻奈が事故に遭った日のことを……",
      "startTime": 101,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 104.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 104.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことがあったんですね……",
      "startTime": 105.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "それなのに不注意で事故を起こしそうになるなんて\n{user}さんが怒るのも当然ですよね",
      "startTime": 112.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 116.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈さんに救ってもらったこの命を\n私はもっと大切にしなくちゃいけないですよね",
      "startTime": 119.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 123.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "これからは気をつけます。心配を掛けてごめんなさい",
      "startTime": 123.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "いや、俺の方こそ怒鳴ったりしてすまなかった",
      "startTime": 128.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 132.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "あの……\nよければ麻奈さんのことをもっと教えてくれませんか？",
      "startTime": 134.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈さんとの楽しかった思い出を聞かせて下さい",
      "startTime": 139.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 143.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "いや、それよりも今はライブの準備をしないと\n今回はさくら達のために特別な演出になってるから……",
      "startTime": 147.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02-skr018.m4a",
      "text": "リハーサルの開始までまだ時間があります\nそれまでの間だけでいいので話を聞かせて下さい",
      "startTime": 155.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 159.23333333333332
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ダメだ\n今は余計なことは考えず、ライブに集中するんだ",
      "startTime": 160.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 164.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02-skr019.m4a",
      "text": "話を聞かないと気になって集中出来ません\nだから麻奈さんのことを聞かせて下さい！",
      "startTime": 168.26666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 171.76666666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02-skr020.m4a",
      "text": "もっと麻奈さんのことを知りたいんです！\nお願いします！",
      "startTime": 174.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "まったく……こんなに強情なさくらもめずらしいな\n仕方がない、リハが始まるまでだぞ？",
      "startTime": 182.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
